  "texts": [
    "To summarize all the results, Table 1 shows the ranking of the five generative models, based on the different metrics FID, IS, Dice and Hausdorff distance.",
    "Here we focus on training segmentation networks with synthetic images only, to not make the table too complicated.",
    "The diffusion model performs best when comparing the models in terms of Dice and Hausdorff distance, but unfortunately this is in several cases explained by memorization.",
    "As expected, the older progressive GAN model often performs worse compared to more recent StyleGAN models.",
    "Overall the rankings are similar for U-Net and the Swin transformer."
  ],
